{"tid":518379,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全球最不快樂地區香港排第7","createTime":"2018-01-03T08:57:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T09:55:22.000Z","uid":28366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"07156d35d2b867a2481e516771530135f9b00e6c","tid":518379,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:57:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/03/165647_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F03%2F165647_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f5930ac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國民調中心蓋洛普發表最新的年度調查報告，結果顯示香港在調查的全球55個國家中，不快樂國家或地區排名第7，淨快樂評分僅得29分(滿分100分)，與南非及土耳其同分，而中國、台灣及澳門均榜上無名。<br />\n<br />\n美國民調中心蓋洛普去年底訪問了全球55個國家及地區、5萬多人，調查他們過去一年的快樂指數、對2018年的經濟及整體展望的樂觀程度。「十大最快樂國家」排首位的是斐濟，淨快樂評分高達92分，其次是哥倫比亞（87分）及菲律賓（84分）。排第4至第10位的，分別是墨西哥、越南、哈薩克、巴布亞新畿內亞、印尼、印度，而阿根廷和荷蘭則並列第10位。<br />\n<br />\n而「十大最不快樂國家或地區」首位是連年戰火不斷的伊朗，淨快樂評分僅得5分，第二位是伊拉克（7分）、第三位則是烏克蘭（8分），第四至第十分依次是希臘、摩爾多瓦、巴西、香港、南非、土耳其及加納。香港、南非及土耳其並列第七位，淨快樂評分僅得29分。<br />\n<br />\n調查在香港以網上形式訪問了500人，發現除了不快樂排名位列全球十大外，香港「淨希望評分」亦只有10分，「淨經濟樂觀評分」更是負11分，兩項評分均在全球較後排名。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180103/57659888\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180103%2F57659888&d=tPtgdxispHM4pG8INjHj0R4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=de754264\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180103%2F57659888&h=91e935ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180103/57659888</a>"},{"pid":"dd22bb5b04f415addf45746c81fac26d6ec99665","tid":518379,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:59:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad184445cc99515494b706d0ca9f70d5986ceae","tid":518379,"uid":19370,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:59:12.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係三甲...<br />\n香港人真係好樂觀"},{"pid":"9f7f1b01c5582a71cd5c3e9b9d5f159a244a7a6d","tid":518379,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ad184445cc99515494b706d0ca9f70d5986ceae","tid":518379,"uid":19370,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:59:12.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係三甲...<br />\n香港人真係好樂觀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T09:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7adcca5e22bee8052ec12cc4fb31ca610813abac","tid":518379,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T09:07:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9c13f7089cdbdbcd701abe8f7ea2638b7dacf0","tid":518379,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T09:17:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"782e7c4628e657d1a8eacfb8f0d252cb0bb634cb","tid":518379,"uid":125464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T09:55:22.000Z","msg":"香港一直以嚟重視既都只係錢 邊個得閒理你快唔快樂<br />\n錢就係衡量所有野既單位<br />\n點為之成功？ 有錢就係成功<br />\n點為之孝順？ 愈多家用就愈孝順<br />\n港好揀老公會唔會唔睇錢？<br />\n當然唔係講緊所有香港人都係咁，但好多由其上一輩既價値觀都係咁<br />\n你想快樂？俾多d心機揾多d錢你就會快樂架啦"}]}